{"lemma":"غَدْرُ","slug":"غَدْرُ","root":"غ.د.ر","root_slug":"غ-د-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/غ-د-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n31489","n31492","n31493","n31494"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%BA%D9%8E%D8%AF%D9%92%D8%B1%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to betray, desert, let down, forsake","tags":["intransitive"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"betrayal, desertion"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n31489","headword_ar":"غدّر","root":"gdr","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He cast"},{"kind":"text","text":"men, or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made"},{"kind":"text","text":"them"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to fall, into what is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gadar","text_ar":"غَدَر"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]; and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Agdr","text_ar":"اغدر","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"may signify the same. (O.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n31492","headword_ar":"غَدَرٌ","root":"gdr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"; pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"guduwrN","text_ar":"غُدُورٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gudorapN","text_ar":"غُدْرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in three places. ―         -b2-  [Hence,] one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aloqati Aln~aAqapu gadarahaA","text_ar":"اَلْقَتِ النَّاقَةُ غَدَرَهَا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The she-camel cast forth what her womb had left remaining in it of blood and foul matter"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"after her bringing forth"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aloqati Al$~aApu guduwrahaA","text_ar":"اَلْقَتِ الشَّاةُ غُدُورَهَا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The ewe,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"she-goat, cast forth the water and blood and other remains in her womb after bringing forth."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY Aln~ahori gadarN","text_ar":"فِى النَّهْرِ غَدَرٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"In the river,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rivulet, is slime remaining when the water has sunk into the earth."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gadarN","text_ar":"غَدَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A place such as is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zalif","text_ar":"ظَلِف"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app. as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hard, and that does not show a footmark,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rugged and hard"},{"kind":"text","text":"],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"abounding with stones:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a place abounding with stones, difficult to traverse:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any difficult place, through which the beast can hardly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in nowise, pass:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"soft ground, in which are"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"trenches,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"channels, such as are termed"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laxaAqiyq","text_ar":"لَخَاقِيق"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"burrows,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lh, S, K, TA,) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"banks,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ridges, worn and undermined by water,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lh, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and uneven"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laxaAqiyq","text_ar":"لَخَاقِيق"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the ground:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lh, S, K, TA: [and the like is also said in the TA on the authority of As:]) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stones"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with trees;"},{"kind":"text","text":"thus accord. to AZ and IKtt: (TA:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"anything that conceals one, and obstructs his sight:"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^agodaArN","text_ar":"اَغْدَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b2-  [Hence,] one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA A^avobata","text_ar":"مَا اَثْبَتَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gadarahu","text_ar":"غَدَرَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA A^avobatahu fiY Algadari","text_ar":"مَا اَثْبَتَهُ فِى الغَدَرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"How firm is he in"},{"kind":"text","text":"traversing"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the rugged and hard and stony place!"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]: this is said of the horse: and also (assumed tropical:)  of the man when his tongue is firm in the place of slipping and of contention or litigation: (S, TA:) or, accord. to Lh, it means (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"how firm,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"valid, is his argument,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"plea, and how seldom does harm in consequence of slipping and stumbling befall him!"},{"kind":"text","text":"or, accord. to Ks,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"how firm is what remains of his intellect"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"understanding!"},{"kind":"text","text":"but ISd says that this explanation did not please him. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"farasN vabotu Algadari","text_ar":"فَرَسٌ ثَبْتُ الغَدَرِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A horse firm,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"steady, in the place of slipping."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ibn-Buzurj, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajulN vabotu Algadari","text_ar":"رَجُلٌ ثَبْتُ الغَدَرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A man firm,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"steadfast, in fight,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"conflict,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, TA,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in altercation"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"disputation,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in speech,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S accord. to different copies,) or and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in altercation"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"disputation,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in speech;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;) and also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in everything that he commences."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.) And accord. to Ibn-Buzurj one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_in~ahu lavabotu","text_ar":"اـِنَّهُ لَثَبْتُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Algadari","text_ar":"الغَدَرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Verily he is strong in talking"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"discoursing, with men,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in contending,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"disputing, with them."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vabotN","text_ar":"ثَبْتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]"}],"source_refs":["S","O","TA","K","Lh"]},{"entry_id":"n31493","headword_ar":"غَدِرٌ","root":"gdr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[part. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gadira","text_ar":"غَدِرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. ―         -b2-  See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gaAdirN","text_ar":"غَادِرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", last sentence but one.       -A2-  And see also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gaduwrN","text_ar":"غَدُورٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".       -A3-  You say also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"layolapN gadirapN","text_ar":"لَيْلَةٌ غَدِرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mugodirapN","text_ar":"مُغْدِرَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K) meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A dark night;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gadoraA='u","text_ar":"غَدْرَا=ءُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (IKtt, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an intensely-dark night,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in which the darkness confines men in their places of alighting"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"abode, and their shelter, so that they remain behind:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or, as some say, such a night is termed ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mugodirapN","text_ar":"مُغْدِرَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"because it casts him who goes forth therein into the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gdr","text_ar":"غدر"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gadar","text_ar":"غَدَر"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (L, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K","IKtt","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n31494","headword_ar":"غُدَرُ","root":"gdr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gudarN","text_ar":"غُدَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gaAdirN","text_ar":"غَادِرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in six places:       -A2-  and for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gudarN","text_ar":"غُدَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", see also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gadiyrN","text_ar":"غَدِيرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}